 -----------------------------------------------------------------------
 Configuration-file for the change_sqlpass Plugin for Squirrelmail
 -----------------------------------------------------------------------

 This configuration file is for the change_sqlpass plugin for 
 Squirrelmail and allows Froxlor users to change their e-mail 
 password within Squirrelmail.

 -----------------------------------------------------------------------

 You only have to edit one thing:

 Look for:

 $csp_dsn = 'mysql://froxlor:MYSQL_PASSWORD@localhost/froxlor';

 and replace MYSQL_PASSWORD with the password for the froxlor-database-user.

 
 If you do not want plaintext-passwords to be stored in the database,
 edit $password_update_queries and remove "password = %5, "
 
